title: Honestly, what do you think is the K-pop group in which the members are just pretending to be friends? - Quora

response.answer_text: I hate to say this as an NCTzen abut I think NCT might be one. The thing with NCT is that there are 21 members and you can't help if all members or some members are just different. Like Ten and Haechan, although they are friends for some reason I keep getting this feeling from them that it's all just for show. I really hate saying this but I think NCT might be one of those groups. But then again they're also plenty of evidence that they are all very close, I just hope we'll get more content with the korean based units of NCT communicating with WAYV members. 💚💚💚 Edit: I 100% agree that they are all close behind camera. This was simply an assumption made by me, I answered this question to point out that that some interactions might've been a bit more exaggerated then how they usually meet. Not saying that they are faking their friendship, but that for fans it might be exaggerated then their usual friendship. I also wanted to point out, that it's unsure whether WAYV and NCT Korea based artists are close. It's been said by the members that they don't often spend a lot of time with each other. Sorry if this offended other fans.

See the thing is most groups are close, that’s just how they are. They are like siblings and when there is a selective few groups that aren’t that close it is shown later in their interactions. For example let’s talk about AOA. Jimin was a mean and horrible leader but most fans couldn’t tell that until Mina (an ex member of AOA) finally went to her social media and posted her story about being bullied for years by leader, Jimin. Here’s the thing, most people probably couldn’t tell because Mina normally was a sweet personality so you would never think someone would bully her, especially someone who is always with her. Jimin was able to mask her true nature behind the leader facade but eventually it was exposed. I really don’t know any other group beside a little something that happened on a v-live with Bangchan, but that’s just a theory. Anyways, if a group isn’t close eventually it will be shown (like Karma), now Jimin has left the entertainment industry and is still getting hate from her rude behavior. Let’s just say she won’t have a future in the music industry anymore. Here’s a group that is like brothers, and they are being goofy!! 😊 But here’s a picture of a group that’s like a family
